| Action | Spot swap |
| From | 500 USDC (`0xaf88d065e77c8cC2239327C5EDb3A432268e5831`) |
| To | WETH (`0x82aF49447D8a07e3bd95BD0d56f35241523fBab1`) |
| Receiver | `0x4E15361FD6b4BB609Fa63C81A2be19d873717870` |
